Demonic Form (Wings)	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.DemonicForm	SOURCEPAGE:p.47	DESC:You may undergo a temporary transformation into a unique demon. Your type changes to outsider with the chaotic, demon, evil, and native subtypes. You gain damage reduction 10/good and cold iron, resistance to acid 10, cold 10, and fire 10, and telepathy to a range of 100 ft. You grow wings and gain a fly speed of 40 ft. with good maneuverability. Your natural weapons, as well as any weapon you wield, are treated as chaotic and evil for the purpose of resolving damage reduction. You can remain in this form for %1 minutes/day; this duration does not need to be consecutive. Returing to your normal form is a free action.|TL-1
Demonic Form (Gills)	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.DemonicForm	SOURCEPAGE:p.47	DESC:You may undergo a temporary transformation into a unique demon. Your type changes to outsider with the chaotic, demon, evil, and native subtypes. You gain damage reduction 10/good and cold iron, resistance to acid 10, cold 10, and fire 10, and telepathy to a range of 100 ft. You grow gills and gain the ability to breath water and a swim speed of 30 ft. Your natural weapons, as well as any weapon you wield, are treated as chaotic and evil for the purpose of resolving damage reduction. You can remain in this form for %1 minutes/day; this duration does not need to be consecutive. Returing to your normal form is a free action.|TL-1
